pmn01a-data-displayed-survey: Iyo mfashanyo ikaba ikozwe mu buryo butaziguye n'ibitigiri vy'abazokwirigwa n'ibitigiri bitangwa n'ikigo c'igihugu. Ni ivyiyumviro vyashikirijwe n'urwaruka mu gihe c'amatohoza, kandi ingingo zose zavuye muri izo nyishu ni zo zitegerezwa kuba ari zo zijejwe uwo mukoresha, atari pmnch. Umugambwe CNDD-SHINGIRO ujejwe kwubahiriza agateka ka zina muntu n'ukwubahiriza agateka ka zina muntu wese. Ivyo vyose vyashikirijwe n'ivyashikirijwe n'abo banyeshure canke ivyashikirijwe n'uwo muhari washizweho n'uwo muhari washizweho n'uwo muhango, bikaba bidahuye n'ivyashikirijwe n'uwo muhari.
